}}'''耳屏'''（英文：Tragus），是[[外耳|外耳]][[耳廓|耳廓]]上的一个小突起[[软骨|软骨]]结构，反向延伸至[[外耳道|外耳道]]口<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Anatomy, Head and Neck, Ear|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470359/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=29262017|first=Alice|last=Szymanski|first2=Zachary|last2=Geiger|access-date=2021-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145619/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470359/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Anatomy of the Ear|url=https://research.nhgri.nih.gov/|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=Online Research Resources Developed at NHGRI|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318000139/https://research.nhgri.nih.gov/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于耳屏朝向后方，有助于[[耳|耳部]]接受后方的[[声音|声音]]信号。相比于前方的声音信号，后方的声音信号在接收上有延迟，这有助于[[大脑|大脑]]辨别前方和后方的声源<ref name="rgate">{{cite journal|title=A numerical study of the role of tragus in the big brown bat|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/8072148|last=Muller|first=Raulf|journal=The Journal of the Acoustical Society of America|publisher=Research Gate|issue=6|doi=10.1121/1.1815133|year=2004|volume=116|pages=3701–12|bibcode=2004ASAJ..116.3701M|pmid=15658720|access-date=13 January 2013}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=External Ear - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/external-ear|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=|publisher=Science Direct|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145541/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/external-ear|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
在[[瘘管|瘘管]]诊断试验中，如患者为阳性（即存在从耳部[[胆脂瘤|胆脂瘤]]到[[骨迷路|内耳迷路]]的瘘），则在其耳屏或周围加压导致的[[外淋巴|外淋巴]]运动可使患者产生[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]或眼球歪斜/[[眼球震颤|眼球震颤]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fistula test {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/fistula-test?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-08|last=Jones|first=Jeremy|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820114307/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/fistula-test?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=How is the fistula test performed in a dizziness evaluation?|url=https://www.medscape.com/answers/1831429-37653/how-is-the-fistula-test-performed-in-a-dizziness-evaluation|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=www.medscape.com|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202071750/https://www.medscape.com/answers/1831429-37653/how-is-the-fistula-test-performed-in-a-dizziness-evaluation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

外耳畸形的种类里包括在耳屏旁出现[[副耳|副耳]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Accessory auricle: Classification according to location, protrusion pattern and body shape|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6177632/|last=Hwang|first=Jungil|last2=Cho|first2=Jaeyoung|date=2018-9|journal=Archives of Plastic Surgery|issue=5|doi=10.5999/aps.2018.00430|volume=45|pages=411–417|issn=2234-6163|pmc=6177632|pmid=30282411|last3=Burm|first3=Jin Sik}}</ref>。

== 其他物种 ==
